    <item>
      <title>本田在华裁员，三家工厂停产</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-11/honda-cuts-jobs-in-china-suspends-production-at-three-plants</link>
      <description><![CDATA[本田汽车公司正在削减工作岗位并暂停其在中国的三家工厂的生产，以寻求削减库存并致力于在全球最大汽车市场进行更广泛的战略转变。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-11/honda-cuts-jobs-in-china-suspends-production-at-three-plants</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Sep 2024 04:01:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>油价跌至每桶60美元，为全球经济软着陆铺平道路</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-11/oil-s-fall-into-60s-widens-runway-for-the-global-economy-to-make-a-soft-landing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[如果一些对石油最为悲观的预测能够成真，那么世界发达经济体或许就有新的理由期待明年经济增长基础更加稳固。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-11/oil-s-fall-into-60s-widens-runway-for-the-global-economy-to-make-a-soft-landing</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Sep 2024 04:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>裕信银行从德国政府手中收购德国商业银行 4.5% 的股份</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-11/unicredit-buys-4-5-stake-in-commerzbank-from-german-government</link>
      <description><![CDATA[意大利联合信贷银行（UniCredit SpA）已收购德国政府出售给德国商业银行（Commerzbank AG）的 4.49% 股份，从而使该意大利银行成为该银行的主要投资者。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-11/unicredit-buys-4-5-stake-in-commerzbank-from-german-government</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Sep 2024 03:50:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
