    <item>
      <title>受房地产市场低迷影响，中国垃圾债券遭遇今年最长跌幅</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-11/china-junk-bonds-suffer-longest-slide-in-year-on-property-slump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国的垃圾美元债券连续七天下跌，为 2023 年 8 月以来最长的下跌周期，此前疲软的房屋销售数据凸显了该国房地产市场低迷的加剧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-11/china-junk-bonds-suffer-longest-slide-in-year-on-property-slump</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Sep 2024 03:42:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哈里斯与支持加密货币的特朗普在辩论中发生冲突，比特币价格下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-11/bitcoin-dips-as-harris-and-pro-crypto-trump-lock-horns-in-debate</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于交易员对美国总统候选人民主党卡马拉·哈里斯 (Kamala Harris) 与共和党对手唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 之间的辩论做出反应，比特币出现下跌，而特朗普对加密货币领域十分感兴趣。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-11/bitcoin-dips-as-harris-and-pro-crypto-trump-lock-horns-in-debate</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Sep 2024 01:51:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>需求担忧加剧油价跌势，油价稳定在 70 美元以下</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-10/oil-stages-rebound-after-global-demand-concerns-trigger-rout</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于对全球需求的担忧迅速升级，引发了油价迅速而强劲的抛售，导致布伦特原油价格两年多来首次跌破每桶 70 美元，随后油价趋于稳定。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-10/oil-stages-rebound-after-global-demand-concerns-trigger-rout</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Sep 2024 23:27:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>交易员消化美国辩论，股市下跌，日元上涨：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-10/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周三亚洲股市下跌，原因是美国通胀报告公布前市场对经济增长的担忧，以及交易员权衡总统辩论的影响。日本央行官员暗示将进一步加息，日元上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-10/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Sep 2024 22:53:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
